{"tid":837064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HK01學晒方向報衰野，疑似用自己報紙走去攻擊同行","createTime":"2018-09-26T05:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T08:58:14.000Z","uid":10014,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d025f82294a4e792db680be9c9ed616d267c68cd","tid":837064,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:55:04.000Z","msg":"近年有不少外賣平台服務興起，其中Plum以提供跨區速遞外賣為賣點，成為打工仔新歡。惟這外賣app近月捲入食物中毒事件，香港01記者追蹤其送餐過程，發現準備時間頗長，由煮好到真正送交客人手上，歷時約2.5小時，部分取餐地點，食物會在烈日下曝曬。食環署共收到43宗對Plum的投訴，並提出兩宗檢控。記者曾向部分餐廳查詢，大部分表示知悉與Plum有合作關係，但沒簽任何合作條款。有大律師表示，本港難有法例監管外賣平台服務，提醒餐廳可要求簽署清晰合約，列明免責條款保障自己。（詳見另文）<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/235118/%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3app-plum%E9%80%81%E9%A4%90%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4-%E7%83%88%E6%97%A5%E6%88%B6%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%96%E9%A3%AF%E7%9B%92-%E7%85%AE%E5%A5%BD%E5%88%B0%E9%80%81%E5%88%B0%E6%AD%B72-5%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F235118%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3app-plum%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%25A4%2590%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25B9%25A4-%25E7%2583%2588%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258F%2596%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E7%259B%2592-%25E7%2585%25AE%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25AD%25B72-5%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582&d=GLlPsK05qGU%2FIJO3gfn48jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4361849e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/235118/%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3app-plum%E9%80%81%E9%A4%90%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4-%E7%83%88%E6%97%A5%E6%88%B6%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%96%E9%A3%AF%E7%9B%92-%E7%85%AE%E5%A5%BD%E5%88%B0%E9%80%81%E5%88%B0%E6%AD%B72-5%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">HK01自己出左個app叫「E肚仔」，係叫用戶落單自取，家下出篇咁既報導擺明就攻擊同行抬高自己</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i